1
00:00:08,420 --> 00:00:10,820
♪Let me write the legend♪

2
00:00:10,820 --> 00:00:13,580
=Young Swordsman=

3
00:00:13,580 --> 00:00:16,580
=Episode 12=

4
00:00:18,679 --> 00:00:21,359
I haven't heard such reckless talk
in a long time.

5
00:00:21,640 --> 00:00:23,519
You may have broken
my Corpse Puppet Formation,

6
00:00:23,519 --> 00:00:25,000
but with your strength,

7
00:00:25,000 --> 00:00:28,079
you won't make it out alive.

8
00:00:31,600 --> 00:00:33,640
Stay out of this,

9
00:00:34,520 --> 00:00:36,840
and I'll spare you and the girl.

10
00:00:37,359 --> 00:00:38,920
What are you trying to do?

11
00:00:39,640 --> 00:00:40,719
Simple.

12
00:00:41,320 --> 00:00:44,159
Kill everyone here,

13
00:00:44,600 --> 00:00:47,200
take their heads,

14
00:00:47,240 --> 00:00:49,520
and offer them to our supreme master.

15
00:00:53,479 --> 00:00:55,079
Then there's no way I'm stepping aside.

16
00:00:55,280 --> 00:00:56,759
You'd risk your life

17
00:00:57,159 --> 00:00:59,200
for these worthless people?

18
00:01:11,439 --> 00:01:12,319
Master,

19
00:01:12,959 --> 00:01:14,760
this bird's wing is broken.

20
00:01:15,079 --> 00:01:16,719
Even if it survives,

21
00:01:16,719 --> 00:01:18,120
it'll never fly again.

22
00:01:18,640 --> 00:01:20,439
Why save it?

23
00:01:21,239 --> 00:01:23,760
Nothing matters more than life.

24
00:01:24,719 --> 00:01:26,920
A life isn't precious

25
00:01:27,239 --> 00:01:29,680
because it can fly high

26
00:01:29,680 --> 00:01:31,280
or because it lasts long.

27
00:01:31,359 --> 00:01:35,760
It's precious because
someone chooses to protect it,

28
00:01:36,280 --> 00:01:39,519
just as I've always protected you.

29
00:01:53,400 --> 00:01:55,680
No one knows better than I do
how precious life is.

30
00:01:57,319 --> 00:01:58,920
I was born with sealed meridians.

31
00:02:00,159 --> 00:02:01,959
My Master spent ten years of inner force

32
00:02:02,799 --> 00:02:05,079
pulling me back from death.

33
00:02:11,159 --> 00:02:14,280
Their lives matter just as much as mine.

34
00:02:23,000 --> 00:02:24,759
That's why I can't step aside.

35
00:02:27,280 --> 00:02:28,759
A dead man walking,

36
00:02:28,759 --> 00:02:30,280
trying to play the hero?

37
00:02:30,560 --> 00:02:33,960
Peng Dasheng,
I thought you were smarter than this.

38
00:02:34,120 --> 00:02:37,520
Turns out you're just as pathetic

39
00:02:37,719 --> 00:02:39,240
and ridiculous as they are.

40
00:02:40,080 --> 00:02:41,120
I'm pathetic?

41
00:02:42,240 --> 00:02:43,639
At your age,

42
00:02:44,080 --> 00:02:45,039
you don't have a single living soul

43
00:02:45,039 --> 00:02:46,360
willing to stand up for you.

44
00:02:46,599 --> 00:02:47,840
You're the pathetic one.

45
00:02:47,840 --> 00:02:48,680
Enough.

46
00:02:49,280 --> 00:02:51,120
I'm done wasting time with you.

47
00:02:51,199 --> 00:02:52,400
Just answer me this.

48
00:02:52,840 --> 00:02:54,919
Even knowing you'll die,

49
00:02:55,439 --> 00:02:57,840
are you still determined
to stand against me?

50
00:02:58,000 --> 00:02:59,159
My master taught me

51
00:03:00,080 --> 00:03:03,360
that those who don't fear death
are the ones who truly deserve to live.

52
00:03:04,199 --> 00:03:05,080
Besides,

53
00:03:07,680 --> 00:03:09,479
what makes you so sure I can't beat you?

54
00:03:10,240 --> 00:03:11,439
Fine.

55
00:03:12,159 --> 00:03:14,840
If you weren't meant
to be my disciple in this life,

56
00:03:15,479 --> 00:03:17,319
we'll meet again in the next.

57
00:03:22,960 --> 00:03:25,759
How is Sang Wuqi so fast?

58
00:03:27,280 --> 00:03:28,800
He's reached the Spirit Roaming Realm.

59
00:03:29,360 --> 00:03:31,960
He's only one step away
from the third rank.

60
00:03:34,520 --> 00:03:36,159
The gap between him and Dasheng
is far too great.

61
00:03:36,159 --> 00:03:38,319
Dasheng is completely outmatched.

62
00:03:49,520 --> 00:03:50,319
Stay back!

63
00:04:04,560 --> 00:04:07,360
Boy, one last time.

64
00:04:07,520 --> 00:04:09,759
Will you back down?

65
00:04:11,159 --> 00:04:12,240
No.

66
00:04:12,560 --> 00:04:13,639
Fine.

67
00:04:14,120 --> 00:04:16,519
Then I'll bleed you dry
one drop at a time

68
00:04:16,879 --> 00:04:19,040
and see how long
you can keep talking tough.

69
00:04:39,199 --> 00:04:42,240
Kneel!

70
00:04:45,920 --> 00:04:46,639
Dasheng!

71
00:04:46,639 --> 00:04:47,639
Stay back!

72
00:04:53,959 --> 00:04:54,959
Old man,

73
00:04:55,879 --> 00:04:57,560
is that all you've got?

74
00:04:58,040 --> 00:04:58,839
Boy,

75
00:04:59,399 --> 00:05:01,360
you haven't disappointed me.

76
00:05:02,040 --> 00:05:03,839
But have you ever considered

77
00:05:04,079 --> 00:05:05,279
that the people

78
00:05:05,279 --> 00:05:06,560
you're risking your life for

79
00:05:06,560 --> 00:05:10,519
once humiliated you,
slandered you, and used you?

80
00:05:11,120 --> 00:05:14,160
Are they really worth dying for?

81
00:05:14,600 --> 00:05:16,759
That's not for you to decide.

82
00:05:18,439 --> 00:05:20,480
Once I start something,

83
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:22,279
I finish it.

84
00:05:22,360 --> 00:05:23,920
Too many deluded fools like you

85
00:05:23,920 --> 00:05:26,040
have corrupted this world

86
00:05:26,199 --> 00:05:27,839
and blurred the line

87
00:05:27,839 --> 00:05:29,040
between right and wrong.

88
00:05:29,920 --> 00:05:32,120
People call the Demon Sect bloodthirsty,

89
00:05:32,199 --> 00:05:34,839
but we only kill those who deserve it.

90
00:05:35,279 --> 00:05:36,399
Peng Dasheng,

91
00:05:36,839 --> 00:05:38,879
you didn't have to die.

92
00:05:39,480 --> 00:05:41,360
I've given you chance after chance,

93
00:05:41,879 --> 00:05:45,480
but you've disappointed me.

94
00:05:54,519 --> 00:05:56,319
If I know I'm doing what's right,

95
00:05:57,639 --> 00:05:59,639
I can die without regret.

96
00:06:03,399 --> 00:06:04,839
What did you say?

97
00:06:06,360 --> 00:06:07,639
I said,

98
00:06:08,800 --> 00:06:11,000
get lost.

99
00:06:11,000 --> 00:06:12,360
Still defiant?

100
00:06:12,360 --> 00:06:13,480
Thunderous Might!

101
00:06:13,680 --> 00:06:15,319
Netherworld Annihilation!

102
00:06:15,560 --> 00:06:17,360
Shatter!

103
00:06:19,079 --> 00:06:19,879
Dasheng!

104
00:06:32,240 --> 00:06:34,279
Now,

105
00:06:34,680 --> 00:06:37,680
break!

106
00:07:00,199 --> 00:07:04,000
How did you
break my Jiuyou Binding Chains?

107
00:07:06,720 --> 00:07:08,800
Dasheng won!

108
00:07:08,800 --> 00:07:10,240
He did it! He won!

109
00:07:12,199 --> 00:07:13,759
He won!

110
00:07:14,879 --> 00:07:16,319
He won!

111
00:07:17,319 --> 00:07:18,279
That's great!

112
00:07:18,759 --> 00:07:23,800
He won! He won!

113
00:07:24,959 --> 00:07:26,399
He won! He won!

114
00:07:28,920 --> 00:07:30,319
- Dasheng!
- Dasheng!

115
00:07:31,600 --> 00:07:32,720
He turned the tables
when all hope seemed lost

116
00:07:32,720 --> 00:07:34,079
and killed a third-rank expert
from the Demon Sect.

117
00:07:34,680 --> 00:07:35,399
Peng Dasheng,

118
00:07:35,639 --> 00:07:36,560
what kind of monster are you?

119
00:07:36,680 --> 00:07:37,279
Watch your mouth!

120
00:07:37,480 --> 00:07:39,279
My young master isn't a monster.

121
00:07:39,279 --> 00:07:40,480
He's a hero!

122
00:07:41,480 --> 00:07:42,079
Yes, a hero.

123
00:07:49,680 --> 00:07:50,759
You... You...

124
00:07:51,800 --> 00:07:52,759
Old man,

125
00:07:53,480 --> 00:07:55,120
do you know where you went wrong?

126
00:07:56,000 --> 00:07:57,759
You underestimated me.

127
00:07:58,040 --> 00:08:00,040
You used all your genuine qi
trying to kill me,

128
00:08:00,519 --> 00:08:02,639
leaving your meridians wide open.

129
00:08:03,240 --> 00:08:05,279
Once I broke free of your formation,

130
00:08:05,600 --> 00:08:07,439
your blood began flowing backward.

131
00:08:07,439 --> 00:08:08,639
Now your body is about to burst.

132
00:08:08,639 --> 00:08:09,439
You...

133
00:08:09,839 --> 00:08:10,199
You...

134
00:08:10,560 --> 00:08:11,160
Save your breath.

135
00:08:12,360 --> 00:08:14,199
Your genuine qi
is about to reach your blood sea.

136
00:08:14,720 --> 00:08:17,519
Any last words?

137
00:08:29,079 --> 00:08:31,399
Peng Dasheng, if I'm going down,

138
00:08:31,399 --> 00:08:33,600
I'm taking you with me!

139
00:08:46,399 --> 00:08:49,639
Not me again!

140
00:08:50,559 --> 00:08:52,440
I'm done!

141
00:08:52,440 --> 00:08:53,679
I want to go home!

142
00:08:53,679 --> 00:08:56,600
I miss my mother!

143
00:08:58,720 --> 00:09:00,559
Father, are you all right?

144
00:09:08,879 --> 00:09:09,679
You're next.

145
00:09:10,360 --> 00:09:13,240
Mr. Peng, we have no grudge.

146
00:09:13,799 --> 00:09:15,559
There's no need to fight to the death.

147
00:09:16,240 --> 00:09:17,440
Why bother talking to her?

148
00:09:17,759 --> 00:09:18,840
Fellow martial artists!

149
00:09:19,039 --> 00:09:19,720
Yes!

150
00:09:19,720 --> 00:09:20,600
Today,

151
00:09:20,600 --> 00:09:21,559
we destroy the Demon Sect!

152
00:09:21,759 --> 00:09:22,679
Destroy the Demon Sect!

153
00:09:22,799 --> 00:09:23,879
Defend the martial world!

154
00:09:24,240 --> 00:09:25,440
Destroy the Demon Sect!

155
00:09:25,440 --> 00:09:26,840
Defend the martial world!

156
00:09:26,879 --> 00:09:28,120
Destroy the Demon Sect!

157
00:09:28,120 --> 00:09:29,399
Defend the martial world!

158
00:09:29,440 --> 00:09:30,759
Destroy the Demon Sect!

159
00:09:30,759 --> 00:09:31,840
Defend the martial world!

160
00:09:32,200 --> 00:09:34,240
Jiuyou Judge? You're alive?

161
00:09:38,840 --> 00:09:40,600
By order of the Demon Sect Leader:

162
00:09:41,360 --> 00:09:42,200
One month from now,

163
00:09:42,720 --> 00:09:46,200
Master Baiyi will be waiting

164
00:09:46,200 --> 00:09:48,320
for all the major sects at Liuchu Manor.

165
00:09:48,639 --> 00:09:52,120
Anyone who disobeys
will be killed on sight.

166
00:09:56,879 --> 00:09:57,559
Dasheng!

167
00:09:58,039 --> 00:09:58,559
Peng Dasheng!

168
00:09:59,159 --> 00:10:00,039
Dasheng, what's wrong?

169
00:10:00,039 --> 00:10:01,679
Don't scare me, Dasheng!

170
00:10:04,840 --> 00:10:05,440
He's fine.

171
00:10:05,559 --> 00:10:06,840
He's just exhausted
and has lost a lot of blood.

172
00:10:06,919 --> 00:10:08,000
He'll recover in a few days.

173
00:10:08,639 --> 00:10:09,720
- All right. Let's go.
- Let's go.

174
00:10:14,240 --> 00:10:15,200
Let's get out of here.

175
00:10:15,200 --> 00:10:16,000
Wait.

176
00:10:17,759 --> 00:10:19,399
Peng Dasheng killed
members of the Demon Sect.

177
00:10:19,559 --> 00:10:21,039
They'll come for revenge.

178
00:10:21,440 --> 00:10:23,519
Keeping him here
at Murong Manor while he recovers

179
00:10:23,559 --> 00:10:25,159
is the best way to protect him.

180
00:10:28,720 --> 00:10:30,279
I doubt my master needs

181
00:10:30,279 --> 00:10:32,399
anyone else's protection.

182
00:10:32,559 --> 00:10:37,360
Could you be Tang Changsheng,
Master of Tang Clan?

183
00:10:37,360 --> 00:10:39,200
That would be me.

184
00:10:39,799 --> 00:10:41,039
Looks like my name

185
00:10:41,039 --> 00:10:43,960
still carries some weight
in the martial world.

186
00:10:45,279 --> 00:10:48,639
Mr. Tang, I heard you retired
three years ago.

187
00:10:48,639 --> 00:10:50,879
What brings you here today?

188
00:10:51,519 --> 00:10:54,759
I'm here for my master,
Peng Dasheng, of course.

189
00:10:57,600 --> 00:10:58,639
Mr. Murong,

190
00:10:58,639 --> 00:11:01,240
would you do me a favor

191
00:11:01,360 --> 00:11:02,639
and let us take him with us?

192
00:11:06,440 --> 00:11:08,200
Thank you, Mr. Murong.

193
00:11:08,399 --> 00:11:09,559
My father is right.

194
00:11:10,480 --> 00:11:11,840
It's dangerous out there.

195
00:11:12,159 --> 00:11:13,960
Staying here is the safest choice.

196
00:11:15,559 --> 00:11:16,360
Xiaojiu.

197
00:11:17,159 --> 00:11:18,080
Let's go.

198
00:11:18,960 --> 00:11:20,200
Don't worry, Miss Murong.

199
00:11:20,360 --> 00:11:22,720
I will keep Dasheng safe.

200
00:11:23,279 --> 00:11:24,080
Farewell.

201
00:11:24,679 --> 00:11:25,720
- Let's go.
- Let's go.

202
00:11:43,519 --> 00:11:45,840
You acted without my permission.

203
00:11:46,440 --> 00:11:50,679
(Master Baiyi, Demon Sect Leader)
Nether Marionette, the penalty is death.

204
00:11:52,120 --> 00:11:53,360
I failed you, Master.

205
00:11:53,960 --> 00:11:56,080
Please punish me.

206
00:11:56,120 --> 00:11:58,320
I still have use for you.

207
00:11:58,960 --> 00:12:00,080
Get up.

208
00:12:00,559 --> 00:12:02,639
Thank you, Master.

209
00:12:04,320 --> 00:12:06,519
Sang Wuqi and his disciples

210
00:12:06,519 --> 00:12:08,720
were all killed by the same man?

211
00:12:08,879 --> 00:12:09,679
Yes.

212
00:12:10,159 --> 00:12:12,200
His name is Peng Dasheng.

213
00:12:12,200 --> 00:12:13,600
He's unknown in the martial world,

214
00:12:13,679 --> 00:12:16,480
but his true strength is hard to gauge.

215
00:12:16,639 --> 00:12:20,080
Sang Wuqi only died because

216
00:12:20,159 --> 00:12:22,399
he underestimated the man and rushed in.

217
00:12:23,000 --> 00:12:25,279
An unknown boy...

218
00:12:25,759 --> 00:12:26,799
How could he kill

219
00:12:26,799 --> 00:12:28,559
a third-rank expert

220
00:12:28,559 --> 00:12:30,600
like Sang Wuqi?

221
00:12:30,799 --> 00:12:33,159
He carries a piece of soul jade.

222
00:12:33,480 --> 00:12:35,960
It's no ordinary jade.

223
00:12:36,559 --> 00:12:39,960
It may explain his incredible strength.

224
00:12:39,960 --> 00:12:44,240
Master, perhaps we should first
look into his background.

225
00:12:44,840 --> 00:12:46,320
No matter who he is,

226
00:12:46,440 --> 00:12:48,679
I won't let him stand
in the way of my plans.

227
00:12:48,679 --> 00:12:50,480
Yes, Master.

228
00:12:52,320 --> 00:12:53,720
Luocha Blade Demon.

229
00:12:55,679 --> 00:12:58,120
(Luocha Blade Demon, Demon Sect)
What are your orders, Master?

230
00:12:58,120 --> 00:13:01,279
Take Gulu and Nether Marionette
and go pay him a visit.

231
00:13:01,600 --> 00:13:02,240
Yes.

232
00:13:03,120 --> 00:13:03,919
As you command.

233
00:13:07,100 --> 00:13:09,260
(Gulu, Demon Sect)

234
00:13:16,660 --> 00:13:19,260
(Su Yeye,
Top Courtesan of Zhenqu Pavilion)

235
00:13:20,720 --> 00:13:22,559
Without my permission,

236
00:13:22,840 --> 00:13:25,039
you dared leave Zhenqu Pavilion.

237
00:13:25,960 --> 00:13:27,120
Su Yeye,

238
00:13:27,440 --> 00:13:28,679
do you know what you've done?

239
00:13:29,200 --> 00:13:30,240
I was wrong.

240
00:13:30,759 --> 00:13:32,240
It won't happen again.

241
00:13:37,360 --> 00:13:39,000
Do it again,

242
00:13:40,039 --> 00:13:42,080
and that delicate skin of yours

243
00:13:42,279 --> 00:13:44,399
will make a fine canvas.

244
00:13:44,679 --> 00:13:47,559
Thank you for sparing me, Master.

245
00:13:50,279 --> 00:13:52,080
Get to Peng Dasheng

246
00:13:52,360 --> 00:13:54,600
before the others do.

247
00:13:54,799 --> 00:13:56,320
If he can be brought over to our side,
keep him alive.

248
00:13:56,799 --> 00:13:58,039
If not,

249
00:13:58,840 --> 00:14:00,039
you know what to do.

250
00:14:00,399 --> 00:14:01,200
As you command.

251
00:14:10,020 --> 00:14:10,500
♪Come on♪

252
00:14:14,020 --> 00:14:15,700
♪This battle, I won't retreat♪

253
00:14:17,660 --> 00:14:20,620
♪In worn-out clothes,
my hem still carries frost and dust♪

254
00:14:20,900 --> 00:14:23,820
♪Among the crowd,
who is laughing at my absurdity?♪

255
00:14:24,060 --> 00:14:26,900
♪They say my birth
has already decided my path♪

256
00:14:27,300 --> 00:14:29,900
♪But I refuse
to believe my birth decides my worth♪

257
00:14:30,420 --> 00:14:33,380
♪With one blade in hand,
I've weathered countless storms♪

258
00:14:33,620 --> 00:14:36,620
♪Covered in scars,
only to be called young and reckless♪

259
00:14:36,780 --> 00:14:39,700
♪If this world only bows
to status and bloodlines♪

260
00:14:39,860 --> 00:14:42,620
♪Then I'll break every rule
with a single slash♪

261
00:14:43,180 --> 00:14:46,500
♪Listen, this heartbeat echoes♪

262
00:14:46,540 --> 00:14:49,540
♪Fate is nothing but a net♪

263
00:14:49,580 --> 00:14:55,220
♪Either be trapped by it
or tear it apart♪

264
00:14:55,620 --> 00:14:57,660
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

265
00:14:58,220 --> 00:15:00,740
♪I don't believe
anyone is born above another♪

266
00:15:01,460 --> 00:15:03,860
♪Even this mortal body
dares to fight back♪

267
00:15:03,980 --> 00:15:07,660
♪I'll step on fate and grow beyond it♪

268
00:15:08,260 --> 00:15:10,380
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

269
00:15:11,300 --> 00:15:13,420
♪Even if the world's cold stares
stand in my way♪

270
00:15:13,580 --> 00:15:16,860
♪This blade will cut through
all worldly judgment♪

271
00:15:16,900 --> 00:15:21,180
♪I am my own king♪

272
00:15:34,260 --> 00:15:35,820
♪I emerge into the world♪

273
00:15:35,820 --> 00:15:37,580
♪Unknown, yet I dare
to shake the martial world♪

274
00:15:37,580 --> 00:15:38,940
♪My pride is my trump card♪

275
00:15:38,940 --> 00:15:40,740
♪Even if fate treats me as worthless,
I refuse to yield♪

276
00:15:40,740 --> 00:15:42,140
♪Born with a gift, I won't give in♪

277
00:15:42,140 --> 00:15:43,900
♪Against heaven's will,
I'll bet on my rise♪

278
00:15:43,900 --> 00:15:45,420
♪A sword in hand,
fresh out of the mountain♪

279
00:15:45,420 --> 00:15:47,140
♪I dare to break every rule♪

280
00:15:47,140 --> 00:15:48,460
♪I see through
the masks of human hearts♪

281
00:15:48,460 --> 00:15:50,300
♪Famous clans are nothing
but a few layers of disguise♪

282
00:15:50,300 --> 00:15:51,540
♪They kneel and beg for fame♪

283
00:15:51,540 --> 00:15:53,780
♪I stand and fight for my dignity♪

284
00:15:53,780 --> 00:15:55,300
♪Facing powerful foes, I will not bow♪

285
00:15:55,300 --> 00:15:56,900
♪With my blade in hand,
I decide what is right♪

286
00:15:56,900 --> 00:15:58,500
♪Stand for justice and never step back♪

287
00:15:58,500 --> 00:16:00,220
♪Even if the whole world
stands against me♪

288
00:16:00,220 --> 00:16:01,940
♪Untamed,
frost has carved me to the bone♪

289
00:16:01,940 --> 00:16:03,300
♪Only then do I become more like myself♪

290
00:16:03,300 --> 00:16:04,940
♪Fight, this life of mine is unyielding♪

291
00:16:04,940 --> 00:16:06,420
♪No matter how dark the martial world,
I'll walk through it♪

292
00:16:06,420 --> 00:16:08,140
♪For love, I do not fight for the world♪

293
00:16:08,140 --> 00:16:09,740
♪I only want
to protect her for a lifetime♪

294
00:16:09,740 --> 00:16:11,300
♪Carefree,
this fleeting life is but a brief stay♪

295
00:16:11,300 --> 00:16:15,620
♪Now I know all things can be overcome♪

296
00:16:15,620 --> 00:16:17,780
♪I raise my blade and change my fate♪

297
00:16:17,780 --> 00:16:20,380
♪Let me write the legend♪

298
00:16:25,260 --> 00:16:27,820
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

299
00:16:27,820 --> 00:16:31,140
♪Win or lose, strong or weak,
none of it matters to me♪

300
00:16:31,140 --> 00:16:33,620
♪Even if I fall, I will still shine♪

301
00:16:33,620 --> 00:16:37,700
♪Let my name
be carved into the vast world♪

302
00:16:38,060 --> 00:16:40,660
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

303
00:16:40,780 --> 00:16:43,140
♪If this world refuses to forgive me♪

304
00:16:43,140 --> 00:16:46,180
♪Then I'll burn away
all my edge and brilliance♪

305
00:16:46,180 --> 00:16:51,220
♪And trade it for a new dawn♪
